###

### 🔎 GET by ID
GET {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/contacts/{{id}}
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### ✏️ PUT update
PUT {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/contacts/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "id": "{{id}}",
  "firstName": "Jan",
  "lastName": "Kowalski",
  "email": "adam@wsei.edu.pl",
  "phone": "123456789"
}

